{"tid":2420017,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【最壞的時代 最好的陪伴】分享下本地流行曲樂嘅嘅新題材：陪伴歌","createTime":"2021-02-23T15:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T05:04:36.000Z","uid":74339,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0cb50ff1c63d256536931ff414f810d0d40c7ca","tid":2420017,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"我聽嘅歌唔多，不過我都想分享下近排自己見到香港流行曲嘅改變。以前嘅香港樂壇嘅流行曲主要得一種題材，就係愛情就唔需要我多講啦。後來都間中有啲叫人做自己嘅歌同埋打氣歌，最好嘅一定會嚟到（？）。例如：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NPa2FCTqd3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNPa2FCTqd3g&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=82b6d0d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NPa2FCTqd3g</a><br />\n青春頌MV - 許廷鏗 (HD)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EbJhct_HTu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEbJhct_HTu8&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=6850534e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EbJhct_HTu8</a><br />\n鄭欣宜 Joyce Cheng - 女神<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tmmliJjsizc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtmmliJjsizc&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=5cfb5d49\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tmmliJjsizc</a><br />\n方皓玟 - 你是你本身的傳奇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wZD_qQ81l3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwZD_qQ81l3Q&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=d26f3b60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wZD_qQ81l3Q</a><br />\nRubberBand -《發現號》<br />\n<br />\n但近呢兩年環境愈嚟愈差，所有嘢都急速惡化，我相信好多人同我一樣對未來都未必咁有信心。然後開始有愈嚟愈多歌係講緊未來係點唔緊要，我都會陪住你。原本呢類型嘅題材都比較非主流嘅歌手唱。例如有我最鍾意嘅：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1lkCjDNDopc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1lkCjDNDopc&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=b621f19c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1lkCjDNDopc</a><br />\nThe Pancakes - Our Gump<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GBbIE6Fyspk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGBbIE6Fyspk&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=ab3a1c34\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GBbIE6Fyspk</a><br />\nSerrini《Let Us Go Then You and I》<br />\n<br />\n但呢類題材嘅歌係2020年之後簡直好似雨後春筍一樣爆出奇多，最出名嘅一定有呢首：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sg8V5BLMEhE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsg8V5BLMEhE&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=406fa334\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sg8V5BLMEhE</a><br />\nDear Jane - 銀河修理員<br />\n<br />\n然後仲有更多更多：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tsL-kPHb0UU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtsL-kPHb0UU&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=ea681483\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tsL-kPHb0UU</a><br />\n林二汶 Eman Lam - 最後的信仰<br />\n<br />\nWyman回應林夕「流淚都必須喝水」嘅：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NR6RZVgQgb0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNR6RZVgQgb0&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=18ca696c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NR6RZVgQgb0</a><br />\n鄭融 Stephanie Cheng《多喝水》<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多其他我自己好鍾意嘅：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4uo685soSGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4uo685soSGc&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=4eec42aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4uo685soSGc</a><br />\nONE PROMISE -《明年見》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gKmajw7QkJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgKmajw7QkJU&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=241273a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gKmajw7QkJU</a><br />\n陳健安 On Chan - 重生 Reborn<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BFdj161FnBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBFdj161FnBs&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=64bb2145\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.